      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "全部仓库"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "All Repos"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Anthropic's API re-reports the cached context on every assistant turn, so the same tokens get counted many times. Turn off to show only “new” traffic (input + output + cache writes). Estimated cost is unaffected.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Anthropic 的 API 会在每轮助手响应时重复报告缓存的上下文，因此同一批令牌会被多次计入。关闭后仅显示“新增”流量（输入 + 输出 + 缓存写入）。估算成本不受影响。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Blend the main detail pane into the sidebar with a soft boundary fade.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
